## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the biopsychosocial model. The complexity of interactions between these factors means that individual experiences can vary significantly. Additionally, cultural interpretations of mental health can differ, affecting the generalizability of some findings. Further research, particularly cross-cultural studies, is needed to deepen the understanding of these interactions.

